name: COVID19ICD10PCSValueSetForCardiacValveReplacement
title: COVID19 ICD10PCS Value Set for Cardiac Valve Replacement
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to cardiac valve replacement and is listed as a cardiovascular disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes aortic, mitral, pulmonary and tricuspid valve replacement.),(Exclusion Criteria: )
